        <h3>
          "Like Lemony Snickets...It's like visiting Disneyland as a child."
        </h3>
        <p>Short Description.</p>
        <div class="visual"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="cta">
    <div>
      <button
        class="main"
        onclick="javascript:document.location='http://eepurl.com/hZq6AH'"
      >
        Subscribe today!
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="principles">
    <div class="wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
      <h1>Principles of Cottage Living</h1>
      <ul>
        <li>Decide the purpose first.</li>
        <li>If the occupant is happy, then it's good design!</li>
        <li>Study the classics, but be bold with form.</li>
        <li>Good design doesn't cost more, it might just take more time.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
